doctor.workplace: Debidwar Ibn Sina Hospital (Pvt.) Ltd, Cumilla
doctor.info: Dr. Md. Abdul Al Wahid is a highly experienced oral and dental surgeon in Cumilla, specializing in smile designing, fixed braces, dental implants, and aesthetic dentistry. With a BDS degree and post-graduate training in oral and maxillofacial surgery, he has also received advanced training in endodontics and cosmetic dental procedures. Dr. Wahid is dedicated to enhancing both oral health and appearance, treating a wide range of conditions including tooth decay, gum disease, root canal infections, misaligned teeth, jaw pain, and discolored or damaged teeth. As a senior dental surgeon at Debidwar Ibn Sina Hospital (Pvt.) Ltd, Cumilla, he combines modern technology with patient-focused care to deliver safe, comfortable, and lasting results. He currently practices at Motiur’s Dental, located within Debidwar Ibn Sina Hospital, where he consults patients from 10:00 AM to 7:00 PM (closed on Fridays). Dr. Wahid is widely trusted for his precision in dental procedures and commitment to creating beautiful, confident smiles.
